1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:40,930
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

3
00:01:40,970 --> 00:01:43,070
[Episode 26]

4
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,759
Where did all these people go?

5
00:01:45,259 --> 00:01:47,460
After fighting, no matter the outcome,

6
00:01:47,530 --> 00:01:49,330
they'd naturally have to leave.

7
00:01:49,660 --> 00:01:50,900
Even if they left right after beating people up,

8
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,229
this is an inn after all.

9
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:53,460
It has been deserted all these years.

10
00:01:53,460 --> 00:01:55,340
You mean no one would have cleaned this up?

11
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,740
So many people died here.

12
00:01:57,770 --> 00:01:59,300
There are also so many talismans downstairs.

13
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,500
They dare not come in?

14
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:01,590
Is there a ghost?

15
00:02:13,210 --> 00:02:15,630
This place is weird and eerie.

16
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:17,290
Let's just go.

17
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:18,980
Wait.

18
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:26,570
Wait.

19
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:28,820
There seems to be a hidden door here.

20
00:02:34,690 --> 00:02:36,420
There are only three of us here.

21
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,500
Why are there a pair of footprints here?

22
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,880
There really is a ghost, huh?

23
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:07,770
What was that?

24
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:08,370
After him!

25
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,670
Let's stop chasing.

26
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:16,360
What on earth was that?

27
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,260
I've never seen this kind of creature before.

28
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:20,330
This is not a normal creature.

29
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:21,540
That's right.

30
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:24,000
Its power and speed are both extraordinary.

31
00:03:24,050 --> 00:03:25,250
We should be careful.

32
00:03:47,390 --> 00:03:48,860
[Elder Shi of Shishou Village]

33
00:03:48,490 --> 00:03:49,570
Who are you?

34
00:03:49,610 --> 00:03:53,870
-We're in the wrong place.
-We're just passing by.
-We're staying the night.

35
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:58,079
There's a ghost inside.

36
00:03:58,270 --> 00:03:59,660
We all dare not come in.

37
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,930
So there is really a ghost after all.

38
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:06,870
S-so there really is a ghost.

39
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,840
Since it was getting quite late,

40
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,880
we wanted to stay the night here.

41
00:04:12,090 --> 00:04:14,870
But we didn't expect that it was pitch dark in here.

42
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:16,180
It's really scary.

43
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,220
Yes, indeed.

44
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:20,220
Lots of people died in this inn many years ago.

45
00:04:20,650 --> 00:04:22,180
You should hurry on out now.

46
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,970
I'm one of the elders of the village.

47
00:04:23,970 --> 00:04:25,089
You are all guests.

48
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:27,140
If you are hungry or tired,

49
00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:29,090
you can stay at my place tonight.

50
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:35,000
We'll take up your offer then.

51
00:04:35,220 --> 00:04:36,150
It's no problem.

52
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:38,430
Useless!

53
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,620
A wandering doctor who doesn't know martial arts

54
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:41,930
and an ignorant rascal taking his first steps in the martial world.

55
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:42,540
If you can't even

56
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:44,180
kill them, then what do I need you for?

57
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:46,740
I’m incompetent. Please punish me.

58
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:47,750
Saintess.

59
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:49,340
If it were only the two of them,

60
00:04:49,340 --> 00:04:50,740
we wouldn't have failed.

61
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,810
Who knew that the lord would be there,

62
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,670
and he even helped them?

63
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:55,990
The lord?

64
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:59,580
I've sent people to look for him everywhere these few days.

65
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:01,040
Why is he with them?

66
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,960
He didn't seem to recognize us.

67
00:05:04,450 --> 00:05:05,380
What did you say?

68
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,790
The lord asked us who we were,

69
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:09,090
and who he was.

70
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,520
He was ruthless when fighting us.

71
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,520
Could it be that the Wuxin Huai

72
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:15,380
made him lose his memory?

73
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:19,700
That day when the man in black injected the Wuxin Huai into the lord's body,

74
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:21,230
I felt something was wrong.

75
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,380
After that, I sent people to look but couldn't find him anywhere.

76
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:25,710
I felt even more uneasy.

77
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:29,160
Looks like something really went wrong.

78
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:36,350
Where are you going, Saintess?

79
00:05:36,350 --> 00:05:38,070
I was just about to settle things out with you.

80
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:38,890
You lied to me.

81
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:41,540
You didn't just give Di Feisheng any regular Wuxin Huai,

82
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:42,870
but the pure Wuxin Huai.

83
00:05:43,659 --> 00:05:45,280
You're planning to overthrow him.

84
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,030
So what?

85
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:49,050
If you dare to hurt him,

86
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:50,570
I'll make you pay.

87
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,220
Di Feisheng only lost his memory for now.

88
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,620
He's not seriously hurt.

89
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,690
On the contrary,

90
00:05:59,050 --> 00:06:01,140
you let the Rama Heavenly Ice fall into others' hands,

91
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:03,340
and caused our plan to fail terribly.

92
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,420
Saintess,

93
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:07,260
can you give me an explanation?

94
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:09,200
It was just a one-off mistake.

95
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,940
I'll take care of it.

96
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:13,050
It's none of your business.

97
00:06:13,170 --> 00:06:13,620
Sure.

98
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,140
I won’t worry.

99
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:17,060
I came here today

100
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,970
to give you a surprise.

101
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:22,880
Do you want to know where Li Xiangyi is?

102
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,280
Li Xiangyi?

103
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:28,970
You tried so hard

104
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,870
to find out where Li Xiangyi is.

105
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:33,140
The spy I planted beside Qiao Wanmian

106
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,490
sent a message back recently,

107
00:06:34,490 --> 00:06:35,900
saying that they discovered the inner breath of

108
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,960
Yangzhouman in Qiao Wanmian's body.

109
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:40,240
There was no such inner breath before.

110
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,260
It was after Qiao Wanmian was poisoned

111
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:43,580
by your Iced Cicada and got cured,

112
00:06:43,930 --> 00:06:45,600
that it suddenly appeared.

113
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,000
Yangzhouman?

114
00:06:49,570 --> 00:06:50,030
No.

115
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,830
The Iced Cicada in Qiao Wanmian's body

116
00:06:54,409 --> 00:06:56,330
was cured by Di Feisheng.

117
00:06:56,659 --> 00:06:58,120
Was it really Di Feisheng?

118
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,659
In this world, the Iced Cicada's poison

119
00:07:00,659 --> 00:07:03,020
can only be cured by Yangzhouman's inner breath.

120
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,590
You know that best.

121
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,470
If it's not Di Feisheng,

122
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:10,360
then there's only one person who was in contact with Qiao Wanmian.

123
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:12,000
Li Lianhua.

124
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:14,980
It really is him.

125
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,310
Li Lianhua

126
00:07:19,220 --> 00:07:20,380
is Li Xiangyi.

127
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:23,870
Di Feisheng is still trying his best to cover up for them.

128
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:25,990
I was devoted to him,

129
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:30,600
and tried to do everything to help him get rid of Li Xiangyi.

130
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:32,820
Not only did he not tell me anything,

131
00:07:33,450 --> 00:07:35,980
but also helped him to lie to me and deceive me.

132
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:40,110
My beautiful Lady Jiao.

133
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:42,409
It seems that your way to win people's hearts

134
00:07:42,409 --> 00:07:44,100
isn't anything worth mentioning.

135
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:45,830
And you don't know a thing about

136
00:07:45,850 --> 00:07:47,700
what they're doing by joining forces.

137
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:48,980
You're really useless as

138
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:52,080
the Saintess of Jinyuan Alliance.

139
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,409
How dare you say anything about me?

140
00:07:58,020 --> 00:07:59,810
If it weren't for your master's sake,

141
00:07:59,810 --> 00:08:01,470
you would have been long dead.

142
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:03,409
Please calm down, Saintess.

143
00:08:03,409 --> 00:08:04,409
It was my mistake.

144
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:06,650
Actually, I'm doing this

145
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:07,890
for your sake too.

146
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:11,380
Di Feisheng has found out about us working together.

147
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:12,840
He couldn't tolerate you.

148
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,270
Isn't it better for him to lose his memory now?

149
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,860
He won't pay attention to both of us,

150
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:19,190
and after you bring him back in the future,

151
00:08:19,730 --> 00:08:21,660
you can train him however you want.

152
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:23,380
According to Master's orders,

153
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,660
what is most crucial now

154
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:26,900
is to first confirm if that person is Li Xiangyi.

155
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:29,030
Then, take back the Rama Heavenly Ice.

156
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:32,020
Your master only asked me to help

157
00:08:32,050 --> 00:08:33,000
and work together with him.

158
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,530
Who is he to order me around?

159
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:37,300
I'll take care of my own matters myself.

160
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:39,100
Since you are his dog,

161
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:41,220
go back and tell him this.

162
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,120
When I come back,

163
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:46,299
I will settle scores with him properly.

164
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:49,419
All of Wansheng Clan is at your disposal.

165
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:58,310
Thank you for letting us stay here tonight, Elder Shi.

166
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:00,820
No one has come to our village for years.

167
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:03,880
It’s a fateful coincidence that you three are here.

168
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:04,820
Elder Shi,

169
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:08,100
have the villagers always been living in seclusion here?

170
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:10,160
It has been more than a hundred years.

171
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:12,300
Our ancestors moved here back then

172
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,580
when fleeing from war.

173
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:16,340
It was only when an outsider came in more than ten years ago

174
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:17,460
that our village had contact

175
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:19,500
with anyone from outside the village.

176
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,300
Come this way.

177
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:28,160
Please have a seat.

178
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:37,070
This is the wild donkey meat that we usually eat in our village.

179
00:09:37,070 --> 00:09:38,940
I don't know if you will like it.

180
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:45,550
I didn’t expect the food in the village to be so abundant.

181
00:09:49,810 --> 00:09:51,330
Thank you, Elder Shi.

182
00:09:51,650 --> 00:09:53,980
But I’ve been praying to Buddha recently.

183
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:56,210
I heard that wild donkeys in the mountains

184
00:09:56,210 --> 00:09:57,500
understand humans very well.

185
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,670
I really can't bear to eat them,

186
00:09:58,670 --> 00:10:00,130
so I'll politely decline.

187
00:10:00,930 --> 00:10:02,000
I see.

188
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:03,980
In that case,

189
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:05,770
please try this Rouchang wine

190
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:08,470
brewed with cold spring water from our village.

191
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:14,560
This young hero here, why don’t you sit down?

192
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:15,990
Elder Shi.

193
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:17,180
To be honest with you,

194
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:19,220
my two brothers here with me

195
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:20,580
are also fasting just like me.

196
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:23,910
So we won't be able to partake in the delicious food and wine.

197
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,500
I see.

198
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,000
Yes.

199
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,200
It is indeed a pity.

200
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,410
Elder Shi,

201
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:32,230
this Rouchang wine you just mentioned.

202
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:34,460
Is it the legendary wine that will

203
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,700
boost the inner power of

204
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:37,970
martial arts practitioners after drinking it?

205
00:10:37,970 --> 00:10:38,770
You are right.

206
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,390
The person who accidentally

207
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,620
entered the village more than ten years ago

208
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:43,280
found that this Rouchang wine

209
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,740
could enhance his power.

210
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:45,810
So,

211
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,840
it attracted many people to come.

212
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,860
But when they knew

213
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:53,440
the Rouchang wine was made from the cold spring in the village,

214
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:55,400
they started to fight for the cold spring

215
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:57,460
and cut down fruit trees to make wine.

216
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,790
The spring dried out,

217
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,220
all the trees were cut down,

218
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:03,700
and the village was left in a complete shambles because of them.

219
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,950
After they left,

220
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:07,380
we blocked off the road to the village.

221
00:11:07,850 --> 00:11:10,530
All these years, besides the three of you today,

222
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:13,540
no one else has ever been here.

223
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:16,480
If the cold spring has dried out for so many years,

224
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,860
[Rouchang wine]

225
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,880
where is this bottle from then?

226
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,460
After so many years,

227
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,940
no one is fighting for the cold spring anymore.

228
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,790
So the spring water in the mountain

229
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,520
slowly revived a little.

230
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,580
The inns in the village were built

231
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:33,310
back then for those martial arts practitioners.

232
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:34,590
After they left,

233
00:11:34,700 --> 00:11:35,970
no one has stayed there since,

234
00:11:35,970 --> 00:11:37,770
which is why it's been deserted.

235
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,510
I see.

236
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:41,140
Elder Shi,

237
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:44,690
what happened in this inn?

238
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:48,350
To be honest,

239
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:49,950
more than ten years ago,

240
00:11:50,050 --> 00:11:51,200
those people from the martial arts world

241
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,280
started a fight in the inn

242
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:56,050
over a little bit of cold spring water.

243
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,620
Much blood was shed.

244
00:11:58,900 --> 00:11:59,970
It's been so long.

245
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,680
Why did no one clean it up?

246
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:04,440
There's a ghost inside.

247
00:12:05,310 --> 00:12:06,170
The villagers were intending

248
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:08,000
to collect the bodies for burial.

249
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,880
But who knew,

250
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:11,230
all the bodies disappeared overnight.

251
00:12:11,690 --> 00:12:13,500
It must be those people who transformed.

252
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,760
They will hurt people.

253
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:17,340
So no one dares to go in.

254
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,860
So that was what happened.

255
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:22,350
Fortunately, we left fast then.

256
00:12:23,370 --> 00:12:23,970
By the way,

257
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:26,010
among the people who came here then,

258
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,820
was there someone who often wore a mask

259
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:28,860
looking like the King of Hell

260
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:31,260
and was called the Lord of the Netherworld?

261
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:34,120
Lord of the Netherworld?

262
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:45,550
There were too many of them coming here back then.

263
00:12:45,740 --> 00:12:47,070
It's been so many years.

264
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,560
I can't remember.

265
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,650
Are you looking for someone?

266
00:12:51,620 --> 00:12:54,460
That man is an old master that

267
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:56,160
my brother here has admired for a long time.

268
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,960
He hasn't met him before either.

269
00:12:58,220 --> 00:12:58,590
Yes.

270
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:00,450
I heard that Master Lian Quan

271
00:13:00,450 --> 00:13:02,380
also drank the Rouchang wine here before.

272
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:04,110
I want to pursue his footsteps,

273
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:06,220
so I'm just taking the chance to ask.

274
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:08,180
I can't help you much there.

275
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,090
It's getting late.

276
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:12,940
Please rest early.

277
00:13:13,380 --> 00:13:16,180
I'll send you out of the village tomorrow morning.

278
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,360
Thank you.

279
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:33,780
Are you hungry?

280
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,730
I'm fasting.

281
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,800
I had to find an explanation you know.

282
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:42,390
On our journey here,

283
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:44,640
