284
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:45,170
Yes.

285
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:46,930
It's strange indeed.

286
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:48,980
The villagers hide when they see us

287
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:49,740
and avoid us.

288
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:52,830
But yet they prepared so much food for us now.

289
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:54,510
It's better not to touch it.

290
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:55,700
So in my opinion,

291
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:57,170
this must be...

292
00:13:57,460 --> 00:13:58,190
A clip joint?

293
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:00,860
You're not being serious again.

294
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:02,420
A clip joint should be located in a place with people,

295
00:14:02,420 --> 00:14:04,420
not in this kind of secluded corner.

296
00:14:05,140 --> 00:14:05,940
Fang Duobing.

297
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,560
Have you heard?

298
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:10,800
Many mountains are inhabited by cannibalistic tribes

299
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:12,840
who only eat humans.

300
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,440
Then the villagers here...

301
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:24,840
This won't do.

302
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,400
Let's go to the kitchen to have a look.

303
00:14:41,930 --> 00:14:43,590
There's nothing here either.

304
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:45,350
Where did they hide the meat?

305
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,620
Since there's something wrong with the food in the village,

306
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:49,910
do you think the Lord of the Netherworld

307
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:51,840
got ambushed after eating the meat

308
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:53,620
and drinking the wine here?

309
00:14:54,450 --> 00:14:55,980
I remember Su Xiaoyong said

310
00:14:55,990 --> 00:14:58,450
they found his last tracks in Shishou Village.

311
00:14:58,450 --> 00:15:00,700
We haven't heard any news about him since then.

312
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:02,560
Did something happen to him here?

313
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:03,820
Indeed, many highly-skilled people

314
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,380
were in that inn earlier,

315
00:15:05,430 --> 00:15:06,930
and there were traces of a fight.

316
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:09,180
But I didn't find any traces of Lian Quan's martial arts.

317
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:09,700
Maybe,

318
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:11,110
he never entered the inn.

319
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:13,580
People usually stop in the inn temporarily.

320
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:14,440
If someone were really

321
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,440
cutting trees and making wine here,

322
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:18,920
they'd have to stay here for a while.

323
00:15:21,110 --> 00:15:23,140
But when we entered the village this afternoon,

324
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:25,220
there were only houses where long-time villagers lived.

325
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:26,580
I didn't see any new houses built

326
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:27,580
by any outsiders.

327
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,620
Could it be the elder that's making things up?

328
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,620
In reality, no one was willing

329
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:32,480
to stay and fight for the spring water to make wine.

330
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,690
Why would she lie?

331
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:38,600
We've all heard stories about this Rouchang wine.

332
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,380
But have you ever thought about

333
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:42,580
whether someone really drank this wine

334
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:44,680
and came to this Shishou Village?

335
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:48,020
You're right.

336
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:48,840
In this world,

337
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,740
there's only ever been tales of this Rouchang wine.

338
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:51,900
But I've never heard anyone claim that

339
00:15:51,900 --> 00:15:52,960
he drank this wine.

340
00:15:53,610 --> 00:15:55,540
If Elder Shi is speaking the truth,

341
00:15:55,580 --> 00:15:57,660
and many martial artist practitioners have been here,

342
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:59,200
there should be many people going around

343
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,410
bragging about it.

344
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:03,560
The Rouchang wine can boost your internal power.

345
00:16:04,170 --> 00:16:05,970
Where did this saying come from?

346
00:16:05,980 --> 00:16:08,040
Many people came here in search of it,

347
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:10,540
but no one has ever returned successfully.

348
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:12,060
I have heard that

349
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:13,790
Tianying Gang once sent disciples

350
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,520
to look for this Rouchang wine.

351
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:18,000
But we don't know what happened after that.

352
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:18,930
Think about it.

353
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:21,980
Everyone who came to this village disappeared.

354
00:16:21,980 --> 00:16:22,980
