355
00:16:25,610 --> 00:16:26,410
This won't do.

356
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:28,640
We'll have to be more alert tonight.

357
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:29,500
We can't sleep.

358
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:33,490
I've always stayed awake in an unfamiliar environment.

359
00:16:35,710 --> 00:16:36,430
Fang Duobing.

360
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:38,100
I'll leave standing guard tonight to you.

361
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:38,880
I'm going to bed.

362
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:40,740
Not like I can do anything if I stay awake anyway.

363
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:41,650
If something really happens,

364
00:16:41,650 --> 00:16:42,650
please act smart.

365
00:16:43,180 --> 00:16:43,670
Wait.

366
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:45,940
Earlier at the inn,

367
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,100
you could tell at a glance

368
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:48,570
the different martial skills from each sect.

369
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:50,460
You're very well-versed in martial arts.

370
