Stop pretending to be modest.

371
00:16:51,990 --> 00:16:53,120
Stay and guide me.

372
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:55,150
Maybe you can even protect me.

373
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,540
If you really want to hear about

374
00:16:57,540 --> 00:17:00,000
