375
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:00,930
of all the sects,

376
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,290
pick a time when the sun is out

377
00:17:02,290 --> 00:17:04,070
and I'll recite everything for you.

378
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:05,620
As for martial arts and fighting,

379
00:17:05,620 --> 00:17:08,100
and protecting everyone's safety, I'll leave it to you.

380
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:09,430
You're the best at this.

381
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,540
This sly old fox.

382
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:13,170
Stop badmouthing me behind my back.

383
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:14,030
You darned fox!

384
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:08,820
Here.

385
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:11,130
I soaked it in water before.

386
00:18:11,130 --> 00:18:11,950
Just make do with it for now.

387
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:12,680
It's edible.

388
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,910
Forget it if you're not eating.

389
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:20,600
Thanks.

390
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,270
You actually took it.

391
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:25,260
I thought a dark-faced fiend like you didn't need any care from others

392
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,920
and didn't care about others.

393
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,810
You're better after losing your memory.

394
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:39,860
You better not touch anything here.

395
00:18:46,100 --> 00:18:46,580
Thanks.

396
00:18:53,080 --> 00:18:54,960
He's not that bad at heart.

397
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:57,810
Maybe we can change him for the better

398
00:18:58,010 --> 00:18:59,410
while his memory is lost.

399
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:04,780
Fei,

400
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:07,500
