401
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:08,300
Martial arts.

402
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,620
Martial arts aren't an aspiration.

403
00:19:10,990 --> 00:19:13,460
Practicing the highest form of martial arts.

404
00:19:13,460 --> 00:19:15,500
There are two types of martial arts practitioners.

405
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:16,380
One of them helps the weak,

406
00:19:16,380 --> 00:19:17,410
