411
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:24,360
It doesn't matter.

412
00:19:28,970 --> 00:19:30,380
Let me rephrase my question then.

413
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:32,900
What will you do if someone

414
00:19:33,210 --> 00:19:33,990
