415
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:34,900
I will kill him.

416
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,220
How can you do that?

417
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:37,380
As the old saying goes,

418
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:38,970
the best thing of a gentleman is to be kind to others.

419
00:19:38,970 --> 00:19:40,460
Acts of kindness need to be accumulated,

420
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:41,520
and acts of evil...

421
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,770
What are you trying to say?

422
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,970
I just want to tell you

423
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:54,540
martial arts practitioners

424
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:55,740
should be righteous.

425
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:57,970
You shouldn't kill for your own selfish desire.

426
00:19:57,970 --> 00:19:59,200
We should help the weak,

427
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,130
and get rid of...

428
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:02,100
I know you once went astray.

429
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:04,010
But who hasn't erred in their life before?

430
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:06,700
The most important thing is to turn over a new leaf.

431
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:07,660
It's fine if you don't want to listen.

432
00:20:07,660 --> 00:20:09,590
But how can you attack me like this?

433
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:18,340
What's that smell?

434
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,110
It's the candle.

435
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:45,150
Something is hidden in the candle.

436
00:20:45,150 --> 00:20:45,950
It's too late.

437
00:20:46,250 --> 00:20:47,450
We inhaled some of it.

438
00:20:52,810 --> 00:20:53,980
It's the Wuxin Huai.

439
00:20:55,370 --> 00:20:56,100
Are you okay?

440
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:57,450
How are you?

441
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,760
What are these things?

442
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:17,840
I don't know.

443
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:28,080
It's the Jade Cloud Bagua Mirror.

444
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:29,360
Could it be the Chief of Cuihua Mountain

445
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:31,090
who went missing ten years ago?

446
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,160
It's the Iron Door.

447
00:21:34,210 --> 00:21:35,740
Blue Wolf Whirlwind Shu Tianhua,

448
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:37,110
and Redface Flying Dagger Zhu Mofei!

449
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:39,150
Are we having a martial arts showdown?

450
00:21:39,150 --> 00:21:40,480
How do you know them all?

451
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:43,380
They are martial art experts who've been missing for years.

452
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:45,260
I can still fight them if it's one by one.

453
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:46,190
But they're coming in hoards.

454
00:21:46,190 --> 00:21:47,610
We'll be ripped to shreds.

455
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:50,070
Channel your energy to force out the poison.

456
00:22:58,950 --> 00:22:59,690
Li Xiangyi?

457
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,750
Li Xiangyi.

458
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:15,930
Li Lianhua!

459
00:23:17,230 --> 00:23:17,890
Li Lianhua!

460
00:23:22,030 --> 00:23:22,960
It's really him.

461
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:25,740
Fang Duobing.

462
00:23:26,530 --> 00:23:28,190
I was scared to death just now.

463
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:30,560
Luckily I hid in time.

464
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,440
A few monsters came here just now.

465
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,360
Who are they?

466
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:36,590
Are you okay?

467
00:23:40,330 --> 00:23:41,660
What could happen to me?

468
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:44,830
No, you...

469
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:46,400
What are you doing?

470
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:47,940
Stop getting your hands

471
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:48,870
