472
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,890
Ridiculous, seriously.

473
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,400
You're like a lunatic.

474
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,880
I'm just worried about you.

475
00:23:57,320 --> 00:23:58,220
There's something wrong with the candle.

476
00:23:58,220 --> 00:23:59,780
Luckily you didn't light it.

477
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:00,520
Luckily for Fei and I...

478
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:02,790
the master in white from last time helped us.

479
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:03,500
Master in white?

480
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:04,700
What master in white?

481
00:24:04,900 --> 00:24:07,550
Have you seen the master in white?

482
00:24:10,030 --> 00:24:11,480
What master in white?

483
00:24:11,650 --> 00:24:13,150
When those monsters came over earlier,

484
00:24:13,150 --> 00:24:14,230
I was scared to death.

485
00:24:14,230 --> 00:24:15,810
I immediately hid behind this door

486
00:24:15,810 --> 00:24:17,410
