487
00:24:17,620 --> 00:24:19,220
Why didn't you come earlier?

488
00:24:24,290 --> 00:24:25,130
Oh, I see.

489
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:27,600
When those people ran away earlier,

490
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,590
