492
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:30,920
We'd better leave now.

493
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:37,950
[Shishou Village]

494
00:24:39,870 --> 00:24:42,720
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

495
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,880
Is your mouth jinxed?

496
00:24:46,910 --> 00:24:47,600
Cut the crap.

497
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:48,170
Fight!

498
00:24:52,410 --> 00:24:53,430
Do you think the master in white

499
00:24:53,430 --> 00:24:54,960
will reveal himself again?

500
00:25:04,220 --> 00:25:04,880
Li Lianhua!

501
00:25:04,950 --> 00:25:05,560
Help us!

502
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,200
Did I guess wrong?

503
00:25:16,730 --> 00:25:18,130
He can't even hold a sword.

504
00:25:18,130 --> 00:25:19,400
He can't be the master in white.

505
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,830
I really can't hold up after

506
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:23,030
just a while of using my internal power.

507
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:35,400
Li Lianhua!

508
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:41,500
Young Hero Lu.

509
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,260
So it's you all.

510
00:25:44,090 --> 00:25:46,150
Let's kill off these monsters first.

511
00:26:04,410 --> 00:26:05,210
Stop chasing.

512
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,570
Wrap up your wounds first.

513
00:26:06,570 --> 00:26:09,030
They are more excited after smelling blood.

514
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:15,810
Thank you for your help earlier, Brother Lu.

515
00:26:15,810 --> 00:26:16,670
I was passing by

516
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:18,340
