00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:40,200
If that's the case,

556
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,200
it would be worse.

557
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:43,740
I don't know where Lianhua is brought to now.

558
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:45,150
He can't even hold a sword now.

559
00:27:45,150 --> 00:27:45,980
If anything happens,

560
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:47,380
he won't be able to fight.

561
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:49,530
I won't let anything happen to him.

562
00:27:51,890 --> 00:27:54,250
Why are you suddenly caring about his safety?

563
00:27:54,250 --> 00:27:55,650
In any case, he can't die.

564
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:57,510
We made such a big ruckus.

565
00:27:57,750 --> 00:27:59,550
But yet the elders and villagers

566
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:00,920
didn't react at all.

567
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:04,080
Are these villagers hiding from these monsters?

568
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:06,700
Kiddo.

569
00:28:06,910 --> 00:28:07,710
Let me ask you.

570
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:08,740
It's dark now,

571
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:10,270
I told you not to run around!

572
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:13,720
No wonder they never go out after dark.

573
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:15,980
It was to avoid these people.

574
00:28:16,330 --> 00:28:18,180
These monsters are all martial experts

575
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,710
who suddenly disappeared.

576
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:22,080
I can't believe they're all here.

577
00:28:22,220 --> 00:28:24,420
Jin Youdao also disappeared suddenly.

578
00:28:24,550 --> 00:28:26,750
He even made plans to meet you around here.

579
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:28,950
Could it be related to this village too?

580
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:30,990
That inn is full of traces of

581
00:28:30,990 --> 00:28:32,530
martial experts fighting.

582
00:28:33,220 --> 00:28:34,300
It must have been moves made by them

583
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:36,220
when they were still sober.

584
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:40,360
But those people obviously already lost their consciousness.

585
00:28:40,390 --> 00:28:43,420
Could they have been lured to this village

586
00:28:43,740 --> 00:28:44,670
and got poisoned

587
00:28:44,780 --> 00:28:45,650
or came down with some illness,

588
00:28:45,650 --> 00:28:47,450
that caused them to be like this?

589
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:48,560
If that's the case,

590
00:28:48,850 --> 00:28:50,850
did that also happen to Brother Jin?

591
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:53,040
This is bad.

592
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,290
Looks like Lianhua also...

593
00:28:55,310 --> 00:28:58,290
Since the people who fought in the inn are still normal,

594
00:28:58,290 --> 00:29:00,020
something must have happened.

595
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:02,790
Is the monster you fought with earlier

596
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:04,350
the same as those in the inn?

597
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:05,960
Let's go take a look.

598
00:29:06,170 --> 00:29:08,170
We should be able to find some clues.

599
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:27,620
Heaven never bars one's way,

600
00:29:28,500 --> 00:29:30,230
or there'd really be no way out.

601
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:42,030
Now it seems that

602
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,990
there are so many talismans here.

603
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,090
These were probably placed by the people living here

604
00:29:45,090 --> 00:29:46,360
to chase away those who lost their consciousness,

605
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:47,370
and repel the evil spirits.

606
00:29:47,370 --> 00:29:49,070
Those people are covered in blood,

607
00:29:49,070 --> 00:29:50,540
and they're even faster than humans.

608
00:29:50,540 --> 00:29:52,740
It's likely that they're treated as ghosts.

609
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:55,470
Could it be that the martial experts staying here

610
00:29:55,850 --> 00:29:57,900
suddenly got attacked by those who came previously

611
00:29:57,900 --> 00:30:00,100
and already lost their consciousness?

612
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:01,470
So that's why

613
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:03,100
such a fierce fight happened here.

614
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:03,960
That means that

615
00:30:04,180 --> 00:30:05,510
people kept coming here

616
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:08,180
and kept getting turned into monsters.

617
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:11,940
Li Lianhua once said

618
00:30:11,940 --> 00:30:14,870
there are traces of Kunlun Sect's martial arts here.

619
00:30:19,340 --> 00:30:19,910
It's him.

620
00:30:20,410 --> 00:30:21,140
I recognize it.

621
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,990
The heavens as palms, and the earth as claws.

622
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:24,660
Is this really Brother Jin's unique skill,

623
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:25,940
the Cosmos Fortune Palm?

624
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,270
Did he really come here?

625
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:29,680
Where is he now?

626
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:30,540
Brother Lu,

627
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:33,500
there are rumors that you are an alcohol fanatic.

628
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:34,700
Do you like drinking?

629
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:35,800
Yes.

630
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,540
But what does it have to do with this?

631
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:39,580
Have you ever heard of

632
00:30:39,580 --> 00:30:41,710
the Rouchang wine in Shishou Village?

633
00:30:41,780 --> 00:30:43,980
This is the legendary Shishou Village?

634
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:45,410
If not?

635
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:51,350
I once told Brother Jin about this Rouchang wine.

636
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,430
Although I don't believe that

637
00:30:52,430 --> 00:30:54,260
the wine can boost internal power,

638
00:30:54,260 --> 00:30:56,570
I heard this wine was made with spring water.

639
00:30:56,570 --> 00:30:58,500
It must be fragrant and delicious.

640
00:30:58,650 --> 00:31:00,380
I've always wanted to taste it.

641
00:31:07,130 --> 00:31:07,860
Brother Jin!

642
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:09,380
I'm here

643
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,510
to remind you

644
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,450
[Cosmos Fortune Palm, Jin Youdao]

645
00:31:12,410 --> 00:31:14,300
about the competition next month.

646
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:17,430
Next month, at the Bahuang Hunyuan Lake at Mount Chrysanthemum.

647
00:31:17,430 --> 00:31:18,490
I'll see you there.

648
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:19,820
Bahuang Hunyuan Lake.

649
00:31:20,010 --> 00:31:20,650
Why there?

650
00:31:21,340 --> 00:31:23,070
You'll know when you get there.

651
00:31:24,130 --> 00:31:25,460
After the competition,

652
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:27,170
I'll gift you something good.

653
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:28,980
Could it be that the gift

654
00:31:29,130 --> 00:31:30,390
Brother Jin wanted to give me

655
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,720
was this Rouchang wine?

656
00:31:31,950 --> 00:31:33,770
So he ran into an accident here

657
00:31:34,670 --> 00:31:36,380
because of this Rouchang wine.

658
00:31:36,380 --> 00:31:37,620
This Rouchang wine

659
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,200
is actually a trick to lure people here.

660
00:31:40,300 --> 00:31:42,220
The reason why no one has said they came to this village

661
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:43,280
and drank this wine

662
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,860
is because everyone who's come here before never made it out.

663
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:48,060
I remember there was a secret door here.

664
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:59,030
There must be something fishy if they have a secret room here.

665
00:31:59,030 --> 00:32:00,630
Maybe we can find some clues.

666
00:32:09,150 --> 00:32:10,610
The mechanism is up there.

667
00:32:14,250 --> 00:32:14,670
Fei...

668
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:32,920
I already knew you were good friends with Brother Li.

669
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:36,180
I didn't expect you and Brother Fei to work together so well too.

670
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:37,380
I don't know him well.

671
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:39,260
Me neither.

672
00:33:21,420 --> 00:33:21,990
Suiyan.

673
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:24,340
It's Nanyin again.

674
00:33:42,540 --> 00:33:44,220
Looks like he died after being decapitated.

675
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:45,660
These clothes are covered with dust.

676
00:33:45,660 --> 00:33:46,610
There's no blood on them

677
00:33:46,610 --> 00:33:48,020
and they are dressed neatly.

678
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:50,700
There are obvious tearing marks where the head was severed off.

679
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,890
This corpse was decapitated

680
00:33:51,890 --> 00:33:52,950
after it dried out.

681
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:54,500
There's no trace of blood around.

682
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:57,960
And the part where the head was severed is also like torn paper.

683
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:05,520
What is this?

684
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:09,760
A ghost entered my house.

685
00:34:09,990 --> 00:34:11,220
These are my last words.

686
00:34:11,220 --> 00:34:12,420
They didn't manage to

687
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:14,150
finish writing this last word.

688
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:17,790
This handwriting...

689
00:34:18,409 --> 00:34:20,969
is the same as that in the room she hung herself.

690
00:34:20,969 --> 00:34:23,370
Looks like this female body was moved here.

691
00:34:23,830 --> 00:34:25,159
But she's already dead.

692
00:34:25,350 --> 00:34:26,739
Why did they dry out her body,

693
00:34:26,739 --> 00:34:27,670
cut her head off,

694
00:34:27,969 --> 00:34:29,199
and hide her body here?

695
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:30,600
And where did her head go?

696
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:41,130
Is this some kind of Nanyin sorcery again?

697
00:34:53,370 --> 00:34:55,030
It's the monster from before.

698
00:34:58,110 --> 00:35:00,510
I seem to have seen this monster somewhere.

699
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:25,060
Elder!

700
00:35:26,450 --> 00:35:26,880
Elder!

701
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:29,350
Elder.

702
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:32,120
We only caught one of the Head God's emissaries.

703
00:35:32,120 --> 00:35:34,780
We didn't manage to get rid of all of them at once.

704
00:35:35,620 --> 00:35:38,390
I didn't expect these people to be so capable.

705
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:41,280
But don't worry.

706
00:35:42,370 --> 00:35:45,390
The inn is the site of nirvana for the Head God.

707
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:48,040
We kept it there for so many years

708
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:50,500
to lure these people in.

709
00:35:52,010 --> 00:35:55,230
We have already prepared the Head Bane there.

710
00:35:55,970 --> 00:35:59,030
Once these people come into contact with the Head Bane,

711
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:02,670
they will become the Head God's emissaries

712
00:36:03,030 --> 00:36:05,560
just like those martial artists from before.

713
00:36:07,570 --> 00:36:09,030
Is this the Head Bane

714
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:12,050
that you're talking about?

715
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:17,270
Nothing happened to you three?

716
00:36:35,410 --> 00:36:36,200
What is this?

717
00:36:37,210 --> 00:36:38,090
So disgusting.

718
00:36:39,210 --> 00:36:40,460
It's human skull bone.

719
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:42,120
The brown liquid on the ground

720
00:36:42,370 --> 00:36:43,410
outside is this.

721
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,280
Mind control bugs?

722
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:53,030
Once they breed these bugs successfully,

723
00:36:53,030 --> 00:36:55,300
they will use it to create all kinds of sorcery.

724
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:57,500
Nanyin people are good at these things.

725
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:59,620
So they cut off the corpses' heads

726
00:37:00,010 --> 00:37:01,250
to breed these bugs?

727
00:37:01,860 --> 00:37:03,060
Mind control bugs...

728
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,660
The mark of the fiend.

729
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:06,990
This is indeed Nanyin's sorcery.

730
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:09,030
Did they become monsters

731
00:37:09,130 --> 00:37:10,420
after getting attacked by these things?

732
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:12,060
First, it was the Rama Heavenly Ice,

733
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:13,010
then the Karmic Bugs.

734
00:37:13,010 --> 00:37:14,470
And now it's these things.

735
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:17,460
What exactly are the Nanyin people up to?

736
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:18,820
In any case,

737
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:20,410
we must find those villagers behind this

738
00:37:20,410 --> 00:37:22,010
and quickly save Li Lianhua.

739
00:37:24,290 --> 00:37:26,690
When we were surrounded by those monsters,

740
00:37:26,750 --> 00:37:29,480
they seemed to avoid the heads that were severed.

741
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:32,900
It's also the human heads that turn people into monsters.

742
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:35,590
Are they afraid of human heads?

743
00:37:38,010 --> 00:37:38,610
I got it.

744
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:41,270
Do you remember those skeleton shadows

745
00:37:41,270 --> 00:37:42,820
we saw at the Bahuang Hunyuan Lake?

746
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:44,730
The reflection of the strange stones on the cliff?

747
00:37:44,730 --> 00:37:45,170
Yes.

748
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:46,580
We always thought

749
00:37:46,650 --> 00:37:48,530
those were just stones that looked like skeletons.

750
00:37:48,530 --> 00:37:50,070
I suddenly realized something.

751
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:52,130
They're using monsters to attack us.

752
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:54,760
But these monsters can't tell what are humans.

753
00:37:54,910 --> 00:37:55,900
How can they be sure

754
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:57,130
they won't get hurt by mistake?

755
00:37:57,130 --> 00:37:58,660
Of course they have to hide.

756
00:37:59,910 --> 00:38:01,570
And they have to hide in a place

757
00:38:01,580 --> 00:38:02,880
where these monsters are afraid of.

758
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,610
Seems like it's not a coincidence.

759
00:38:04,610 --> 00:38:05,260
Those stones

760
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:07,580
are not naturally occurring strange stones,

761
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:09,940
but are actually human heads covered in mud

762
00:38:09,940 --> 00:38:11,070
and hung on the cliff

763
00:38:11,460 --> 00:38:12,860
to ward off the monsters.

764
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:14,290
Yes.

765
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:16,670
They must be hiding nearby.

766
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:23,230
You didn't get struck by the Head Bane?

767
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:26,430
Do you want us to also become neither human nor ghost?

768
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:29,580
You...

769
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:31,960
How dare you insult the Head God!

770
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:32,940
Head God?

771
00:38:33,450 --> 00:38:34,980
It's just a corpse that breeds the mind control bugs,

772
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,430
and yet you worship it as a god.

773
00:38:36,430 --> 00:38:37,280
How foolish.

774
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:38,950
Go!

775
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:40,970
Get back the Head God!

776
00:38:41,500 --> 00:38:42,520
Get it back now!

777
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:52,580
Looks like you're really afraid of these ceramic pots.

778
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:55,180
If the emissaries of the Head God find you here,

779
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,770
they will tear you apart.

780
00:38:56,890 --> 00:38:57,970
Let us go now!

781
00:38:57,990 --> 00:38:59,100
Those Head Gods of yours

782
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:00,700
are afraid of the human skulls here.

783
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:01,410
They won't come in.

784
00:39:01,410 --> 00:39:02,010
Am I right?

785
00:39:02,520 --> 00:39:02,980
Tell me.

786
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:05,050
Where did you take Lee Lianhua?

787
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:07,550
What's the point of asking that now?

788
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:10,130
As long as they are captured by the Head God's emissaries,

789
00:39:10,130 --> 00:39:11,860
they won't live for more than two hours.

790
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:14,510
I'm afraid he's already dismembered by now.

791
00:39:14,690 --> 00:39:15,360
You...

792
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:19,330
If you want to know where the Head God's emissaries are,

793
00:39:19,610 --> 00:39:20,360
dream on.

794
00:39:23,810 --> 00:39:24,940
If you don't tell me,

795
00:39:25,370 --> 00:39:27,170
I'll put this on you

796
00:39:27,690 --> 00:39:29,950
and make you the Head God's emissary too.

797
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:31,140
What do you think?

798
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:40,740
Wait.

799
00:39:56,100 --> 00:39:57,090
Don't go any further.

800
00:39:57,090 --> 00:39:58,290
Don't go any further.

801
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:02,540
That is where the Heaven and Earth Pit is.

802
00:40:02,970 --> 00:40:04,900
It's where they make the Head Bane.

803
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:08,010
The Head God's emissaries have taken over the place.

804
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:09,410
How can we control them?

805
00:40:09,470 --> 00:40:11,710
There's nothing we can do.

806
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:14,350
Only when the sun shines into the cave,

807
00:40:14,410 --> 00:40:16,070
they'll become dull-witted.

808
00:40:16,620 --> 00:40:17,420
Otherwise...

809
00:40:18,180 --> 00:40:19,710
Otherwise, there's no way.

810
00:40:20,060 --> 00:40:20,950
Just wait for a bit more.

811
00:40:20,950 --> 00:40:22,550
When the sun shines into the cave,

812
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:23,280
you can go in.

813
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,600
This is Li Lianhua's bag.

814
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:30,900
With every minute of delay,

815
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:33,030
Li Lianhua will be in even more danger.

816
00:40:34,060 --> 00:40:34,590
Let's go.

817
00:40:48,140 --> 00:40:48,800
Li Lianhua!

818
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,330
Li Lianhua, wake up!

819
00:40:58,090 --> 00:40:58,750
Li Lianhua!

820
00:41:00,650 --> 00:41:02,110
Why is there so much blood?

821
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:03,770
Please be okay.

822
00:41:04,550 --> 00:41:06,030
I still have a lot to ask you.

823
00:41:06,030 --> 00:41:06,560
Lianhua,

824
00:41:08,140 --> 00:41:09,020
don't die.

825
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:10,420
I still have a lot to ask you.

826
00:41:10,420 --> 00:41:11,280
Stop making so much noise.

827
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,590
I'm not dead yet.

828
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,270
I'm just sleepy.

829
00:41:17,250 --> 00:41:18,180
You're fine?

830
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:20,060
You even fell asleep?

831
00:41:20,260 --> 00:41:21,620
Why are you sleeping here?

832
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:22,220
Don't shout. Come on.

833
00:41:22,220 --> 00:41:22,820
